funkjs

A sweet selection of JavaScript funky function extensions that let you do all sorts of nice things when coding JavaScript.

funk.chain
~~~~~~~~~~

  Chain many functions together


  Example uses:

    Do something after a method has been called:

    obj.doSomething = funk.chain(obj.doSomething, function(){ 
      /* do something else after */ 
    });
  
  
    Do something before a method has been called:
  
    obj.doSomething = funk.chain(function(){ 
      /* do something before */ 
    }, obj.doSomething);

